----------------
css
----
    - CSS stands for Cascading Style Sheets
    - CSS describes how HTML elements are to be displayed on browsers screen
    - css saves a lot of work

    Examples:
            <html>
                        <head>
                                <style>
                                        p{
                                                text-align: center;
                                        }
                                </style>
                        </head>
                    <body>
                            <p> I am Paragraph1 </p>
                            <p> I am Paragraph2 </p>
                            ....
                            <p> I am Paragraph10 </p>
                    </body>
            </html>
            Refer programs CSS1.html

            CSS Selectors
            -----------------
                    - element Selector
                            - the style are given to the spcific HTML element only
                                Examples:
                                        h3{
                                                text-align: center;
                                                color: red;
                                         }
                    - id selector
                             - The id selector usees the id attribute of a HTML element to
                                select a specific element
                                refer program CSSID.html
                    - class selector
                                - The class selector elements with a specific attribute
                                - The class selector restricts that thr styles need to be used by the specific
                                  HTML element only
                                    Refer program CSSClass.html

                    - grouping selector

                                Example:
                                        h3{
                                              text-align: center;
                                              color: blue;
                                        }
                                        h4{
                                                text-align: center;
                                                color: blue;
                                        }
                                        p{
                                                text-align: center;
                                                color: blue;
                                        }
                                        After grouping
                                                h3,h4,p{
                                                        text-align: center;
                                                        color: blue;
                                                }
            Ways of Inserting CSS
            ----------------------
                                - Internal Styles sheet
                                            - The styles are defined using <style> tag in <head> section
                                            - The styles are used only within the some HTML file
                                            - all above programs are internal

                                - Inline styles sheet
                                           - The styles are defined using "style" attribute along with the HTML element
                                           - The styled are used only within the some HTMl element
                                                        Refer Program CSSInline.HTML
                                - External Styles sheet
                                            - The styles are defined in external css File
                                            - The styles are used in othe HTML files
                                                    Refer Program
                                                            - mystyle.css(External css file)
                                                            - externalCSS.HTML(External css file)





